{"root":{"data":{"id":"djhylauw89s0","created":1782373266594,"text":"AC6321A8智能电度表","font-size":24},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhym1w4gw00","created":1782373325441,"text":"计量电路（BL0942）","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhytu08mo80","created":1782373935189,"text":"火线锰铜分流器差分对接至计量芯片--IP/IN，检测输入电流，计算压降反馈给MCU","priority":null,"progress":2,"font-size":16},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhzcoj7h2w0","created":1782375412194,"text":"BL0942-Pin4通过电压采样检测交流电压，同时MCU-PA5检测电压变化（1. 过零保护；2. 极速掉电检测。）","priority":null,"progress":2,"font-size":16},"children":[]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhym2mju600","created":1782373327039,"text":"继电器驱动电路（MD7620A）","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhzm4fuycw0","created":1782376152098,"text":"正向脉冲：PA3高电平，PA4低电平, 持续50-100ms；OA输出12V, OB输出0V，线圈得电，磁铁极性变化，继电器闭合。","progress":2,"font-size":16},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhzr8rmoi80","created":1782376553338,"text":"反向脉冲：PA3低电平，PA4高电平，持续50-100ms；OA输出0V，OB输出12V, 线圈得电，磁铁极性改变，继电器断开。","layout_right_offset":{"x":13.000000000000227,"y":0},"progress":2,"font-size":16},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djhzskrwmk80","created":1782376657840,"text":"状态保持：若PA3/PA4,同时输出高电平或低电平，则继电器状态保持。","font-size":16},"children":[]}]}]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhym3rycj40","created":1782373329543,"text":"漏电保护电路","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dji0fhxf5y80","created":1782378454019,"text":"PA9高速采样通过漏保的电流，若检测漏电电流>30mA, 则触发中断，PA3低电平，PA4高电平，使继电器断开火线。","progress":2,"font-size":16,"layout_right_offset":{"x":41,"y":0}},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhym45l07k0","created":1782373330367,"text":"蜂鸣器电路","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"dji0rjnb49k0","created":1782379398131,"text":"PA9模拟PWM 发送2K-4KHz方波信号，蜂鸣器发声","progress":2,"font-size":16},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djhz76who680","created":1782374981995,"text":"按键","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djikse2oj0g0","created":1782435886562,"text":"PA0/PB8/PB9检测到低电平，MCU做出对应按键指令","progress":2,"font-size":16},"children":[]}]},{"data":{"id":"djilbpyfe6g0","created":1782437401345,"text":"屏幕显示","font-size":18},"children":[{"data":{"id":"djilbwmdv940","created":1782437415855,"text":"IIC通信协议","font-size":16},"children":[]},{"data":{"id":"djilbxvmwb40","created":1782437418591,"text":"UART串口协议","font-size":16},"children":[]}]}]},"template":"right","theme":"fresh-blue","version":"1.4.43"}